{"tid":672358,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[科幻美劇]Westworld 《西部世界》S2","createTime":"2018-05-21T02:37:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T03:47:52.000Z","uid":20430,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0ad057bbc8ecb18d86c1840236b796e8716a5e84","tid":672358,"uid":20430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T02:37:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTien41mg76RWVPJMo0ZCCFS3480PomH3ag3G22_T052aBS5GISzQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcTien41mg76RWVPJMo0ZCCFS3480PomH3ag3G22_T052aBS5GISzQ&h=578056d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n劇集來源<br />\n《西方極樂園》是一部於HBO播出的美國科幻西部電視劇，由強納森&middot;諾蘭和妻子麗莎&middot;喬伊共同創作，改編自美國小說家麥可&middot;克萊頓導演和編劇的1973年科幻電影《鑽石宮》，以及較少程度的1976年續集《未來世界》。這是第二次根據兩部電影改編的電視劇，第一次是一部短暫的1980年影集《西部之外》。<br />\n<br />\n故事內容 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">S1劇透</span></span><br />\n《西部世界》（Westworld）講述在未來世界有著一個龐大的高科技成人主題樂園，裡面有六個主題園區，而劇中圍繞的當然是「西部世界」園區；第一季講到園區內機械人們自我覺醒，脫離編寫好的故事和程序，而這正正與樂園創造者和他的搭檔留下的謎團「迷宮」有關。第一季故事線眾多﹑錯綜複雜，各個懸念在季末揭露讓人極為震撼，現在進入第二季故事，迷團進一步加深。"},{"pid":"02eaacc6526e471ee01dabb3dfe7a18b7443e0d3","tid":672358,"uid":20430,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T02:46:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/gQ1e4YXsygWe1cNulJuYmA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzAwO2g9MzAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/news.knowing.asia/362632ab82a75c64157b37e715839a67\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FgQ1e4YXsygWe1cNulJuYmA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzAwO2g9MzAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fnews.knowing.asia%2F362632ab82a75c64157b37e715839a67&h=f4c51b89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n樂園西部世界接待員機械人Dolores，演員Evan Rachel Wood。扮演著機械果份冰冷感覺真係好利害，前半部同後半部角色發展都對演員演技好有挑戰。"},{"pid":"6dd044075e10488f7f3c3af1d95ad730d741a933","tid":672358,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T02:48:28.000Z","msg":"又開"},{"pid":"8a3330a75e6378e332ff6e051f5ae5f4f37d6f64","tid":672358,"uid":20430,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T02:57:27.000Z","msg":"未睇過套劇講乜？<br />\n<br />\n未來人類建立左一個園區，稱為樂園。遊客(即人類)進入樂園可以自由體驗世界，想做乜都無問題，就好似玩電腦遊戲GTA咁，殺人放火強姦乜都得，你覺得前面的機械人接待員樣衰？客人大可舉槍轟頭烯巴爛，機械人有血有肉四飛，畫面真實感是賣點。想淫慾一番？可以到妓女館享受一下。遊戲點玩無明確方向，遊戲想隨便殺人(指接待員)又得，跟遊戲發展故事線也可以。"},{"pid":"31062d87ba2d7775b4722fec2b60f5af15437556","tid":672358,"uid":20430,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6dd044075e10488f7f3c3af1d95ad730d741a933","tid":672358,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T02:48:28.000Z","msg":"又開"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T02:58:40.000Z","msg":"見S1都無人講，S2開返個<br />\n巴打有無睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bc9897ea08381987b80274548a4e7ffc54da461","tid":672358,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31062d87ba2d7775b4722fec2b60f5af15437556","tid":672358,"uid":20430,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6dd044075e10488f7f3c3af1d95ad730d741a933","tid":672358,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T02:48:28.000Z","msg":"又開"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T02:58:40.000Z","msg":"見S1都無人講，S2開返個<br />\n巴打有無睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T02:59:44.000Z","msg":"s1 s2都有人開咗劇情討論區<br />\n我s2停咗2集無睇"},{"pid":"71d85049bfda2ad384d51b6c59fc97c1c69abbf0","tid":672358,"uid":124450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T03:46:47.000Z","msg":"Hi Dad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13361a6206b3a1448fdf9e9c4e8fce4ea7b42eec","tid":672358,"uid":2811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T03:47:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/634494/page/34\" target=\"_bla